09/25/2025,748.2003(b)(4) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,10/02/2025,10/02/2025,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,No,During an investigation it was observed medications are being prepared several days in advance prior to administration. ,"The operation emailed to following compliance into licensing :

THE MARS HAVE BEEN UPDATED TO INCLUDE PRESCRIBING MD INFORMATION AND EACH MAR HAS THE SIGNATURE PAGE ATTACHED AND SIGNED by each staff administering medications, 

THE MEDICATION WITH INACCURATE COUNT WAS CORRECTED IMMEDIATELY DURING THE VISIT ON 9/25/2025.

STAFF  WAS RE-TRAINED ON PROPER DOCUMENTATION OF COUNT IN THE LOG BOOK ON 9/25/2025 AT 5:30PM.

ALL PILLS WERE RETURNED FROM LABELED PILL BOXS TO ORIGINAL BOTTLES AND ALL STAFF WAS IMMEDIATELY TRAINED ON ADMINISTERING MEDICATIONS -ON 9/26/2025 AT 2PM FOR MORNING SHIFT , AND AGAIN AT 6PM FOR EVENING SHIFT.
