08/05/2025,748.303(a)(10)(A) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,08/26/2025,08/22/2025,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,Yes,"Based on a review of documentation, it was determined that a child's unauthorized absence was not reported Licensing within the required timeframe.","08/22/2025-The operation's Governing Body submitted to licensing staff via email the operation's Corrective Action Plan indicating as of 08/06/2025, the Governing Body updated internal procedures as well as communicated with all staff regarding updated unauthorized absence procedures requirements based on the operation's policies.

According to the operation's Governing Body, all staff (including 24-Hour Awake Overnight Staff) has been directed to report all unauthorized absences to Licensing by contacting the Intake Hotline within 2-Hours of unauthorized absence in minimizing future risk of non-compliance.




"
08/05/2025,748.303(a)(10)(B) - Individual Standards Evaluated,Individual Standards Evaluated,No,08/26/2025,08/22/2025,Individual Standards Evaluated,Medium,Yes,"Based on a review of documentation, it was determined that a child's unauthorized absence was not reported to the parent within the required timeframe.","08/22/2025-The operation's Governing Body submitted to licensing staff via email the operation's Corrective Action Plan indicating as of 08/06/2025, the Governing Body updated internal procedures as well as communicated with all staff regarding updated unauthorized absence procedures requirements based on the operation's policies.

According to the operation's Governing Body, all staff (including 24-Hour Awake Overnight Staff) has been directed to report all unauthorized absences to parent(s) by contacting the Intake Hotline within 2-Hours of unauthorized absence in minimizing future risk of non-compliance.




"
